trans-unit.source:
FactoryTypeInformation: Added support for Zope3 style factories.
If the &lsquo;product&rsquo; property of a type info instance is empty the &lsquo;factory&rsquo;
property is interpreted as an IFactory name.

Tools and PortalFolder: Removed support for deprecated marker attributes.
&lsquo;_isDirectoryView&rsquo;, &lsquo;_isPortalRoot&rsquo;, &lsquo;_isTypeInformation&rsquo; and &lsquo;_isAWorkflow&rsquo;
are no longer supported.

TypesTool: Pass &lsquo;object&rsquo; through to TypeInformation objects&rsquo;
&lsquo;listActions&rsquo;.
(<a href="http://www.zope.org/Collectors/CMF/482">http://www.zope.org/Collectors/CMF/482</a>)
